currentdescription: Design, Construction, Supply, Testing and Commissioning of Piped Water Supply Schemes for habitations left out under Har Ghar nal Ka Jal nischay yojna in areas having ground water quality issues; with Electric Driven Pumps and Iron (Strike off irrelevant impurity) Removal Treatment Plant having Technology (Adsorption/ Ion exchange/ Membrane/ Nano Technology/etc.) certified by CSIR or any other institute of national repute. In Garhiya Baluwa, Jhunnikala, Khokha South, Khutti Haseli, Panchyat of Srinagar Block (Total-8 Nos. Schemes) in  the District of Purnea Bihar on turn-key basis with 06 months Trial Run Period and Comprehensive Operation and Maintenance of 60 months under Mukhyamantri Grameen Peyjal Nishchay Yojna (Quality Affected) Under  P.H. Division, Purnea.
